409
00:21:16,360 --> 00:21:17,000
(Just two)

410
00:21:17,080 --> 00:21:18,240
(ordinary travelers then?)

411
00:21:26,760 --> 00:21:27,200
Hurry up.

412
00:21:38,560 --> 00:21:39,080
Lei Wujie.

413
00:21:39,800 --> 00:21:41,200
You said you would bring me to Xueyue City.

414
00:21:41,880 --> 00:21:42,480
But you

415
00:21:42,480 --> 00:21:44,080
