713
00:36:08,360 --> 00:36:09,280
I'm just

714
00:36:11,080 --> 00:36:12,040
an innkeeper

715
00:36:12,240 --> 00:36:13,280
who knows many things.

716
00:36:17,080 --> 00:36:18,280
So where are we going?

717
00:36:18,960 --> 00:36:19,920
Jiulong Sect?

718
00:36:21,600 --> 00:36:23,680
Belle's Manor of Three-Gaze City.

719
00:36:25,280 --> 00:36:26,280
Three gazes.

