822
00:40:36,240 --> 00:40:37,360
If you want to gamble, you stay.

823
00:40:37,760 --> 00:40:39,760
If you don't want to gamble, please leave.

824
00:40:40,760 --> 00:40:41,960
You must be joking, Fairy Rui.

825
00:40:42,360 --> 00:40:43,520
Two pearl boxes

826
00:40:43,560 --> 00:40:45,000
are enough to reserve the entire manor?

827
00:40:45,640 --> 00:40:46,520
He looks

828
00:40:46,640 --> 00:40:47,880
